            As regards the point made by the noble Lord, Lord Hylton, about the side note and so on, I am advised that it is in order and that the intentions of Clause 12&#x2014;to cover the registration of bands taking part in public processions&#x2014;are clear enough as the clause is drafted. That is the advice I have been given.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0583P0-01772'>
