            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_79gc' title='Col. 79GC &mdash; HL Deb 13 November 1997 vol 583 c79GC' name='column_79gc' href='#column_79gc' rel='bookmark'>79GC</a>
            constable should do anything other than pour it down the drain immediately. I suspect that is the answer we will get from the Minister today.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0583P0-01788'>
        <a name='S5LV0583P0_19971113_GCR_125'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-alderdice' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0583P0_19971113_GCR_125' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Alderdice' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
